Class AbstractSignalData

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.alasca.physical_data.TimedEntity
      • fr.sorbonne_u.alasca.physical_data.AbstractSignalData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimingI, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComposedSignalData, SignalData

    public abstract class AbstractSignalData
extends TimedEntity
    The class AbstractSignalData is the common type of all signal data, be it single or composed.
